Fix-Discord-Font

This is to revert back to a nicer discord font, why? CUZ GG SANS LOOK TERRIBLE. I got most of the code from @TheCommieAxolotl#0001 so this wouldn't have been done without his awesome coding. I got it from his theme called Ultra! You can get this theme here: https://thecommieaxolotl.github.io/BetterDiscord-Stuff/Ultra Anyways, I hope this solves the font problem and you guys enjoy! Have fun!!!
